                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6350" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0993</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9160 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">以审计促保护：YL天池保护区绩效审计之辩</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Promoting Protection through Auditing: Debate on the Performance Audit of YL Tianchi Reserve</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孔莉，刘同州，侯新润，吴黎彦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南云龙天池国家级自然保护区管护局</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公共管理和社会组织</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">环保部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">自然保护区；绩效审计；资源环境审计</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Natural Reserve; Performance audit; Resources and environment audit</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019年6月，中央审计委员会印发《关于深入推进审计全覆盖的指导意见》指出进一步拓展审计监督广度和深度，消除监督盲区，做到应审尽审、凡审必严，在促进生态环境保护等方面起到有效监督作用。而自然保护区是生态建设的核心载体，在维护国家生态安全中居于首要地位，同时投入巨额的财政资金，但却面临着审计监督的缺位，在Y省也是如此。D州审计局利用这次契机，提出开展自然保护区绩效审计这一新型审计方式，考虑到自然保护区绩效审计和以往的资源环境审计有本质不同，州审计局组织专家展开了论证。本案例重现自然保护区绩效审计的论证过程，以及D州审计局积极响应中央号召，立足实际、履职尽责、守正创新的探索，以引导学生关注不同审计方式的优缺点，并从自己角度为各方做出选择。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In June 2019, the central audit committee issued the guiding opinions on further promoting full audit coverage, which pointed out that we should further expand the breadth and depth of audit supervision, eliminate the blind spot of supervision, ensure that all audits should be done and strict, and play an effective supervisory role in promoting ecological and environmental protection. The nature reserve is the core carrier of ecological construction, which plays a primary role in maintaining national ecological security. At the same time, it has invested a huge amount of financial funds, but it is facing the absence of audit supervision, which is also the case in Y province. D state audit bureau took advantage of this opportunity to put forward a new audit method to carry out the performance audit of nature reserves. Considering that the performance audit of nature reserves is essentially different from the previous resource and environment audit, the State Audit Bureau organized experts to demonstrate. This case reproduces the demonstration process of the performance audit of the nature reserve and the D state audit bureau&#39;s active response to the call of the central government, based on reality, due diligence, integrity and innovation, so as to guide students to pay attention to the advantages and disadvantages of different audit methods and make choices for all parties from their own perspective.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《审计理论与实务》，《政府审计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宏观环境的含义；G-PEST分析法；自然保护区绩效；审计的含义；鱼骨图分析法；审计目标的含义及确定原则；3E理论；5E理论；审计内容的含义</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-06</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
